title: PW Package Mechanical Drawing
summary: Mechanical outline drawing for a 16-pin leaded package with top/side/detail views and dimensional tolerances.

structured_data.description: Shows body dimensions (e.g., width around 6.2-6.6 mm and length around 4.3-4.5 mm), lead geometry, seating plane, pin-1 index area, and detail-A lead profile.
